    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 997.2-generation Carrera S, a pinnacle of mechanical engagement. This example features the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, delivering 385 hp with linear power delivery and factory-corrected IMS reliability. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, the drivetrain is paired with a mechanical limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing a 10mm lower ride height and sophisticated adaptive damping. Every bushing, seal, and fluid service is current, maintaining strict factory tolerances. The coachwork retains its original luster with consistent paint depth, and the cabin shows zero bolster wear or switchgear delamination. A truly turnkey, investment-grade driver\u2019s machine.",
